{
  "stem": "1873.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a place where a German could be easily called in and killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody will see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Leon Feldhendler, although he was from Zolkiewka, but he lived in Izbica, and was a friend of my dad, so he did know me very well.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you see, the younger kids were able-- there was a few of us young people-- we were able to move around more easier than the grownup people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I did know about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He told me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Leon called  me, and he told me in that we are doing this and this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember, on the 13th of October, because there are windows, and somebody could look in inside, push the papers, everything, push against the windows, and nobody could look in.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they want to kill a German over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We would call him under pretense that something is wrong with the ovens, something is cracking, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When he will come in, we can-- well, of course, otherwise, I wouldn't let anybody in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he told me, Kali Mali will come with-- Kali Mali is a name of a Russian prisoner of war who was in the organization.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He will come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he will hide behind the oven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when the Nazi comes in, you show him, so he should turn his back to the Jews, hidden Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he will be killed with an axe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so I was aware of what's happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was very much scared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember the plan was, actually, that after we assembled for the rollcall, which would take place 5:30, we should wait till 5:30, because some Germans could survive.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And at that point, they will notice that another friend is missing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
